WEBVTT

00:00.876 --> 00:02.795
Go on about the wigmakers.

00:03.045 --> 00:03.921
I would. . . .

00:05.005 --> 00:07.341
I've gotta go have
my pacemaker checked.

00:07.549 --> 00:10.010
It's been so exciting talking to you.

00:10.636 --> 00:14.181
A: You don't have a pacemaker.
And B: I'll be back tomorrow.

00:15.641 --> 00:18.185
Tomorrow is promised to no one.

00:21.522 --> 00:22.773
Goodbye.

00:27.778 --> 00:29.863
Pacemaker, my ass.

